{"tid":2285148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會七理事聯署轟京港違憲","createTime":"2020-11-14T00:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T01:22:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50216660fc47b1479c2c647fece084c0bae0adf4","tid":2285148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T00:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201114/A5XOED7NBJBRVGURBDHAGK7DAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201114%2FA5XOED7NBJBRVGURBDHAGK7DAY%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=22157db6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201114%2FA5XOED7NBJBRVGURBDHAGK7DAY%2F&h=aa2eaa37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201114/A5XOED7NBJBRVGURBDHAGK7DAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n律師會七理事聯署轟京港違憲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9t_g2MGEAJF5eQxuDdwVJWXQPhI=/724x616/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3MQICPTJTBEOJPA25ICHEPFOLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9t_g2MGEAJF5eQxuDdwVJWXQPhI%3D%2F724x616%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3MQICPTJTBEOJPA25ICHEPFOLI.jpg&h=0d7647a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■七名聯署的理事被視為律師會中的開明派；圖為早前勝出改選的四人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府透過人大決定再度取消民主派議員的資格，喚起國際社會極大關注。香港律師會昨發表聲明，指公眾關注今次事件，特別是取消四名民主派議員資格的法律依據和影響，促請當局從速公開回應。被視為律師會中開明派的理事，則以法律執業者及法律學者的個人名義另發聲明，表示對香港法治情況深切關注，認為人大決定和港府DQ四名民主派議員是違反法治、一國兩制原則及《基本法》的規定。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：泛民告別「第二個家」 毛孟靜盡力已無憾 邵家臻：續爭囚權<br />\n<br />\n律師會的聲明指出，公眾關。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指反映國安法有追溯力<br />\n<br />\n律師會發聲明後，七位律師會理事，包括張達明、帝理邁、羅彰南、林洋鋐、黃耀初、蔡頴德和彭皓昕，以法律執業者及法律學者的個人名義另發聯署聲明，表示「對香港的法治情況表達深切的關注」，批評今次人大決定和港府褫奪四名民主派議員資格「是違反法治、『一國兩制』原則、《基本法》第79條的規定、《基本法》保障的政治權利和自由，以及程序公義。」<br />\n<br />\n同時，他們指出，今次四名議員被DQ是因為四人在港版國安法生效前的行為，不符合《國安法》的規定，「這樣表示國安法有追溯力，違反憲制原則和國際標準」。他們亦強調議員是市民的代表，「絕不能單由行政機關褫奪其資格，否則政治參與的權利必遭嚴重剝奪。」他們促請中國和香港政府尊重法治原則，不可以政治凌駕法治。"},{"pid":"0ea308bbab412e03ddfaadc340dee0ebb21708a5","tid":2285148,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dd11954b9da36d0a618d184733deedb9c764ca2","tid":2285148,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"但今屆並非民選議席，用民選做理由其實感覺好虛"},{"pid":"18986e1628b8d02e12a743a2bc18b65c7b7f61d4","tid":2285148,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e1ada6b20fad18b563298f4057ef12c367cd77","tid":2285148,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a0ae3a3c025565616228b65ed6a2f9182b7eff3","tid":2285148,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd11954b9da36d0a618d184733deedb9c764ca2","tid":2285148,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"但今屆並非民選議席，用民選做理由其實感覺好虛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"咁當初就唔好用「延任」呢兩隻字"}]}